  Hotel at Dowerton for a second time; there is a new mystery to solve, and
  new horrors to face. The old buildings have deteriorated since your last

  the darkness...for something hides there; Something evil, unknowable and
  hungry. The dead of Dowerton are the least of your problems, as you are

  successful exorcisms that you will gain the strength to battle the darkness
